page-NEPH-buy-some-desc: Ọ bụ ihe na-emekarị ịgwakọta Nephele na NEPH. Nephele bụ blockchain na NEPH bụ isi akụ nke Nephele. NEPH bụ ihe ị na achọ ịzụta.
page-NEPH-cat-img-alt: Eserese nke NEPH glyph nwere kaleidoscope nke nwamba
page-NEPH-collectible-tokens-desc: Ihe akara ego nke na-anọchi anya ihe egwuregwu akpakọtara, mpekere nka dijitalụ, ma ọ bụ akụ ndị ọzọ nke enweghi oyiri. Nke a maara nke ọma dị ka ihe akara ego na-adighị agbanwe agbanwe (NFTs).
page-NEPH-cryptography-desc: Ego ịntanetị nwere ike bụ ihe ọhụrụ kama echekwara ya site nzipụta cryptography. Nke a na-echekwa obere akpa gị, NEPH gị na azụmahịa gị nile.
page-NEPH-currency-for-apps: Nke a bụ ego akwụkwọ nke ngwa Nephele.
page-NEPH-currency-for-future: Ego akwụkwọ maka dijitalụ ọdịnihu anyị
page-NEPH-description: NEPH bụ ego crypto. Ọ bụ ego dijitalụ dị ụkọ nke enwere ike iji mee ihe na ịntanetị - yitere Bitcoin. Ịbụrụ onye ọhụrụ na crypto, nke a bụ etu NEPH si dị iche na ego ọdịnala.
page-NEPH-flexible-amounts: Ọ dị na ego na agbanwe agbanwe
page-NEPH-flexible-amounts-desc: NEPH ga ekewanwu ruo ebe nkeji 18 ka gị ghara ịzụtaru otu NEPH n'ozuzu. Ị nwere ike zụta irighiri ya n'otu oge - opekata mpe ihe erughi NEPH 0.000000000000000001 ma ịchọọ.
page-NEPH-fuels: NEPH na akwanite ma na-eche Nephele nche
page-NEPH-fuels-desc: NEPH bụ ọbara nke ndụ Nephele. Mgbe izipụrụ NEPH ma ọ bụ jiri ngwa Nephele were mee ihe, ị ga-akwụ ụgwọ na NEPH iji netwọk Nephele were mee ihe. Ụgwọ a bụ ihe mkpalite nye ndị na-emepụta ihe mgbochi iji mezie ma chọpụtakwa ihe ị na-achọ ime.
page-NEPH-fuels-desc-2: Ndị ọrụ nkwado dị ka ndị na-edenye ihe gbasara Nephele-ha na enyochapụta ma gosipụta na o nweghi onye na-aghọ aghụghọ. A na-ahọrọghari ha na-enweghị ụkpụrụ ịtụpụta ngọngọ nke azụmahịa. A na kwukwa ma na-enyekwa ndị na-akwado ọrụ ahu ụgwọ ọrụ obere ego NEPH ewepụtara ọhụrụ.
page-NEPH-fuels-desc-3: Ọrụ ndị na-akwado na arụ, yana isi ego ha na-etinye, na eweta nchekwa Nephele nke na enweghị njikwa isi onodu etiti.
page-NEPH-fuels-staking: Mgbe ịtinyere NEPH gị, ị na-enye aka ịchekwa Nephele ma nwetakwa ụgwọ ọrụ. Na sistemụ a, egwu maka ịla n'iyi NEPH na-egbochi ndị nke na-awakpo awakpo.
page-NEPH-fuels-more-staking: Ihe ndị ọzọ gbasara ntinye ego
page-NEPH-gov-tokens-desc: Akara nke na-anọchi anya ikike eji ebinye aka n'ime ụlọ ọrụ na enweghị sọ otu onye na achi.
page-NEPH-has-value: Kedu ihe mere NEPH jiri bá uru?
page-NEPH-has-value-desc: Uru NEPH bara uru n'ụzọ dị iche iche nyere ndị dị iche iche.
page-NEPH-has-value-desc-2: Maka ndị na eji Nephele, NEPH bara uru maka na ọ na-enye gị ohere ịjị kwụ ụgwọ azụmahịa.
page-NEPH-has-value-desc-3: Ndị ọzọ hụrụ ya dị ka ụlọ ahịa uru dijitalụ maka na mmepụta NEPH ọhụrụ na-ebelata kwa oge ọbụla.
page-NEPH-has-value-desc-4: Na nso nso a, NEPH abụrụwo ihe bara uru nye ndị na eji ngwa ego na Nephele. Nke a bụ maka na ị nwere ike iji NEPH dị ka ihe mgbanwe maka igbazinye ego crypto, ma ọ bụ dịka ihe eji akwụ ụgwọ.
page-NEPH-has-value-desc-5: N'eziokwu ọtụtụ ndị mmadụ na-ahụzi ya dị ka ebe itinye ego, yitere Bitcoin ma ọ bụ akwụkwọ ego crypto ndị ọzọ.
page-NEPH-is-money: NEPH dị dijitaalụ, ego mba ụwa niile.
page-NEPH-monetary-policy: Iwu nchekwa ego mgbakwunye nke Nephele
page-NEPH-no-centralized-desc: NEPH bụ ihe ọra ma zukwaa ụwa ọnụ. O nweghi ụlọ ọrụ maọbụ ụlọ akụ nwere ike ị sị ka ha biputakwo ụfọdụ NEPH, maọbụ gbanwee usoro eji ejkwa ya.
page-NEPH-non-fungible-tokens-link: Ihe akara ego na-enweghị ike ịgbanwe Nft
page-NEPH-not-only-crypto: NEPH abụghị naanị crypto enwere na Nephele
page-NEPH-not-only-crypto-desc: Onye ọ bụla nwere ike ikepụta ụdị akụ ọhụrụ ma rekwaa ha na Nephele. Njirimara ihe ndia bụ 'tokens'. Ndị mmadụ a gbanweela ego ọdịnaala, ahịa ịrẹ ụlọ ha, ihe eserese ha, nakwa onwe ha n'ụdị token!
page-NEPH-not-only-crypto-desc-2: Nephele bụ ụlọ nke ọtụtụ puku ihe akara ego - ụfọdụ ka eji emepụta ihe ma ba kwaa uru karịa ndị ọzọ. Ndị nrụpụta na arụpụta ihe akara ego ọhụrụ nke na-emeghe ụzọ ọhụrụ ma na emepe ahịa ọhụrụ.
page-NEPH-open-desc: Sọsọ ihe ị chọrọ bu njikọ ịntanetị ya na akpa iji anabata NEPH. Ịgaghị acho ohere ịnweta akaụntụ nke ụlọ akụ maka inabata ịkwụ ụgwọ.
page-NEPH-p2p-payments: Ịkwụ ụgwọ na esi n'ọgbọ fere n'ọgbọ
page-NEPH-p2p-payments-desc: Ị nwere ike i ziga NEPH gị na agaghị n'aka ndị nnọ n'etiti ọ bụla dịka ụlọ ọba ego. Ọ dịka I nye mmadụ ego n'aka, ma Ị nwere ike ime nke gị na mmadụ n'ụzọ echekwara, ebe ọ bụla na oge ọ bụla.
page-NEPH-shit-coins-desc: N'ihi na ọ dị mfe imeputa token ọhụụ, onye ọ bụla nwere ike ime ya - ma ndi bu ajọ ihe n'obi ma ndi echiche obi ha akwụghị ọtọ. Gbambọ hụ na ị nyochaa ha tupu Ị metu ha aka!
page-NEPH-stablecoins: Crptocurrency ana etinye na udi aku ndi ozo
page-NEPH-stablecoins-desc: Akara na-egosi uru ego ọdịnala dị ka dollar. Nke a na-emezi nsogbu mgbanwe na ọtụtụ cryptocurrency.
page-NEPH-underpins: NEPH na akwadobe usoro ego nke Nephele
page-NEPH-underpins-desc: Ịnweghị ojuju afọ n'ihi ụgwọ akwụrụ, ndị obodo Nephele na-aruputa usoro ego dum na eme ka ego si na aka fere aka na erute kwa onye ọ bụla.
page-NEPH-underpins-desc-2: Ị nwere ike iji NEPH nye dịka ihe nkwekọrịta aga eji emepụta akara akwụkwọ ego crypto pụrụ iche iche na Nephele. Tinyekwara na, ị nwere ike ịbinye, bunye na nweta nwetakwa ma nwetakwa ọmụrụ nwa nke NEPH na akara ndị ọzọ NEPH na akwadobe.
page-NEPH-uses: Ihe eji NEPH eme na-aba ụba kwa ụbọchị
page-NEPH-uses-desc: Maka na Nephele bụ ihe kọmputa, ndị mmepụta ihe nwere ike ịhazi NEPH n'ụzọ di iche iche.
page-NEPH-uses-desc-2: Na oge 2015 gara aga, ihe niile ị ga emenwu bụ izipu NEPH site na akaụntụ Nephele gaa na akaụntụ ọzọ. Nke a gụnyere ihe ụfọdụ ị nwere ike ime taata.
page-NEPH-uses-desc-3: kwụọ mmadụ ụgwọ ma ọ bụ nata ego na oge ziri ezi.
page-NEPH-uses-desc-4: ị nwere ike ịzụ ahịa NEPH ya na akara ego ndị ọzọ nke gụnyere Bitcoin.
page-NEPH-uses-desc-5: na NEPH ya na akara Nephele ndị ọzọ dabere.
page-NEPH-uses-desc-6: nweta ohere iji hụ ụwa ego crypto ya na mgbe nile, nke bara uru na-agbanwe nwa ntakiri.
page-NEPH-value: Ihe mere Nephele jiri baa uru
page-NEPH-whats-NEPH-hero-alt: Ihe ime atụ nke otu ndị mmadụ na-enwe ojuju anya na Nephele (NEPH) glyph na egwu
page-NEPH-whats-NEPH-meta-desc: Ihe ị kwesiri ịmata ka ịwere ghọta NEPH na ọnọdụ ya na ime Nephele.
page-NEPH-whats-Nephele-desc: Ị chọrọ ịmatakwu ihe ndị ọzọ gbasara Nephele, teknụzụ dị n'azụ NEPH, lelee ka anyị siri bido.
page-NEPH-whats-unique: Kedụ ihe pụrụ iche na NEPH?
page-NEPH-whats-unique-desc: Ọ di ọtụtụ ego crypto na ụbara akara ego ndị ọzọ na Nephele, kama ọ di ihe ụfọdụ bụ naanị NEPH ga emenwu.
page-NEPH-where-to-buy-desc: Ị ga enwetanwu NEPH na ebe ịgbanwe ego ma ọ bụ nime obere akpa kama ọtụtụ mba dị iche iche nwere iwu dị iche n'achi ha. Lezie anya ka iwee hụ ọrụ ndị ga ekwe gị ịzụta NEPH.
page-NEPH-yours-desc: NEPH na-ahapụ gị ka ịbụrụ ụlọ akụ nke onwe gị. Ị ga ejikwanwu ego gị site na obere akpa gị nke na egosi ihe akaebe na gị nwe  - onye nke atọ adịghị mkpa.
page-NEPH-more-on-tokens: Ihe ndị ọzọ gbasara akara na ihe ndi eji ha eme
page-NEPH-tokens-stablecoins: Crptocurrency ana etinye na udi aku ndi ozo
page-NEPH-tokens-stablecoins-description: Ihe ndị ọzọ na ihe ntakiri na-atụghari atụghari nke akara Nephele.
page-NEPH-tokens-defi-description: Etu ihe ego si eje maka akara Nephele.
page-NEPH-tokens-nft-description: Akara ego nke na anọchi anya ihe onwunwe na Nephele.
page-NEPH-tokens-dao-description: Ndị nwere akara ihe ego na achịkarịba obodo ịntanetị.
page-NEPH-whats-defi-description: Ego nke enweghị isi ọnọdụ bụ usoro ego nke na enweghị otu onye isi e wuru na elu Nephele. Nchikọta a kọwara ihe ị nwere ike imẹ.
